br /&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: 12px; color: gray;"&gt;（使用&lt;a href="https://fetchrss.com/feedLink?w=67d7ba1d141b09f2900edc32" target="_blank"&gt;FetchRSS&lt;/a&gt;生成的提要）&lt;/span&gt;</description><pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.rand.org/pubs/research_reports/RRA4737-1.html</guid></item><item><title>如何避免与朝鲜发生意外核战争</title><link>https://www.rand.org/pubs/commentary/2026/03/how-to-avoid-an-accidental-nuclear-war-with-north-korea.html</link><description>&lt;img height="90" src="https://www.rand.org/content/rand/pubs/commentary/2026/03/how-to-avoid-an-accidental-nuclear-war-with-north-korea/_jcr_content/par/teaser.crop.160x90.cm.jpeg/1774315999773.jpeg" width="160" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p class="desc"&gt;金正恩不会参与旨在剥夺他认为可确保国家生存的核能力的讨论。将外交重点转向政治和经济措施，以及采取措施减少意外核战争的风险，可能会让他回到谈判桌。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: 12px; color: gray;"&gt;（使用&lt;a href="https://fetchrss.com/feedLink?w=67d7ba1d141b09f2900edc32" target="_blank"&gt;FetchRSS&lt;/a&gt;生成的提要）&lt;/span&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.rand.org/pubs/commentary/2026/03/how-to-avoid-an-accidental-nuclear-war-with-north-korea.html</guid></item><item><title>海岸警卫队水道安全风险评估工具回顾</title><link>https://www.rand.org/pubs/research_reports/RRA3612-1.html</link><description>&lt;img height="90" src="https://www.rand.org/content/rand/pubs/research_reports/RRA3612-1/_jcr_content/par/teaser.crop.160x90.cm.jpeg/1774300222722.jpeg" width="160" /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;p class="desc"&gt;作者评估了美国海岸警卫队 (USCG) 使用的水道安全风险评估工具组合，重点关注用于改进 USCG 水道安全风险评估的工具和选项的碎片化和重叠。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;span style="font-size: 12px; color: gray;"&gt;（使用&lt;a href="https://fetchrss.com/feedLink?w=67d7ba1d141b09f2900edc32" target="_blank"&gt;FetchRSS&lt;/a&gt;生成的提要）&lt;/span&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 23 Mar 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.rand.o